    "shortCode":  "DYRfwdSum1V",
    "caption":  "What started as a journey to support and empower women in Iten is now growing into something much bigger 💜\n\nToday, we are proud to officially introduce Tulizo Foundation — a movement dedicated to creating safe spaces, empowering women and girls, supporting athletes, and bringing conversations around gender equality and gender-based violence into the wider community.\n\nThrough sport, education, mentorship, school outreach, and community engagement, we hope to create long-term positive change where it matters most — at the grassroots level.\n\nWe are also incredibly grateful to officially partner with the ASICS Foundation as we begin this journey together. This partnership gives us hope, strength, and the opportunity to expand our postive  impact within the community.\n\nThis is only the beginning. 🌍✨\n\n#TulizoFoundation #RunForChange #CommunityImpact #WomenEmpowerment #Iten GenderEquality SafeSpaces ASICSFoundation\n\n🎥 🥰 @the.adventure.bakery",
